{"tid":132014,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"泳衣女Fans危站海旁︰Leon換走了我的眼睛","createTime":"2017-02-23T13:26:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-25T14:07:17.000Z","uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7b9b2d562fdd22d68fc897876054e0dda3003348","tid":132014,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T13:26:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170223/large/1487855211_a213.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170223%2Flarge%2F1487855211_a213.jpg&h=28b12adf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nLeon黎明明晚將於中環海濱活動空間舉行《Leon's Penguins in Live 香港演唱會》，Leon下午5時許乘車抵達會場，在舞台對出空地巡視，並唱歌試音響。其間，有瘋狂粉絲於海旁危站想睇綵排，並指被黎明換走了眼睛，要求見黎明。<br />\n<br />\n事發於晚上7時許，會場外的海旁位置，一名內地女子身穿泳衣、披著一條紅色毛巾，冒著寒冷天氣危站海邊欄杆外，狀甚危險，保安員見狀上前勸止。其後，內地女向保安表示要見Leon，「他(Leon)換走了我的眼睛，然後我看到的太陽，看到的月亮，就跟你們看到的不一樣」，「我要黎明過來把眼睛還給我」，保安員擔心她會墮海，繼續游說她返回安全位置，內地女聞言即回應︰「反正我發誓我不會跳下去，okay？」並表明一定要見Leon，「他不來我才跳下去，我等到明天他開完演唱會」，保安員苦勸不果，報警求助。警員接報到場，勸服該名內地女返回安全位置，再由救護車送院檢查。<br />\n<br />\n讀者許先生，事發時做完運動，剛巧路經上址，看見該名內地女身穿泳衣站於欄杆外，不斷說要見Leon，而且將行李及個人物品散落地上。"},{"pid":"5d108d50d3f3b1c5d651e012499da8e1a1283faa","tid":132014,"uid":33053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T13:29:06.000Z","msg":"睇錯左泳兒女fans"},{"pid":"825867c46f49b0a18db6b33d7969aa93596af3f6","tid":132014,"uid":17263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T13:34:45.000Z","msg":"寫輪眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8249b684d8d1973c4df1b7029b75e230b1a403b","tid":132014,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T13:35:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇錯左泳兒女fans</blockquote><br />\n+1<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b326d46f7301afef2988d05082843a0955745f94","tid":132014,"uid":48579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T17:00:34.000Z","msg":"我愛黎明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"160f285fa6acb393b3482c509876491c0037dcb6","tid":132014,"uid":59639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T17:09:40.000Z","msg":"换咗眼睛 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後見到人壽命"},{"pid":"b1beff7ab5325d3f1497b6341ed71aad540bd10a","tid":132014,"uid":36478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T19:49:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我愛黎明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/iXWWMwp2wPg/maxresdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FiXWWMwp2wPg%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg&h=7f466aea&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"97440090ded1771c6e415783e4018c1ea2640af5","tid":132014,"uid":64250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T13:56:38.000Z","msg":"我眼睛想旅行"},{"pid":"640ad98aef459cc25e3aaa7f24344a58eef35bfe","tid":132014,"uid":48124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T14:07:17.000Z","msg":"如果想開心，為什麼需要等<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}